    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A range of dark reddish colors resembling the colors of the garnet mineral, particularly the gem-quality stone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
